paper/review/rendered.txt-700-7 Limitations
paper/review/rendered.txt:701:The credibility tiers and realization distribution are judgment priors with no literature calibration;
paper/review/rendered.txt-702-the ordering is defensible, the levels are not measured, and the stance sweep is the honest bound
paper/review/rendered.txt-703-on their influence. The QALY lens counts only health, so the estimate is a floor on total wellbeing,
paper/review/rendered.txt-704-and the causes where Scott concentrates — education, mobility, equity — are precisely those
paper/review/rendered.txt-705-whose main benefits the lens excludes. Credibility shrinks toward zero but never below it,
--
paper/review/rendered.txt-719-real total; re-deriving in real dollars moves shares by hundredths of a percentage point. The
paper/review/rendered.txt-720-geography audit’s scalar U.S. shares and regional decompositions were reconciled separately
paper/review/rendered.txt-721-and can differ by fractions of a point per organization. Finally, several anchors rest on a small
paper/review/rendered.txt-722-number of quasi-experimental papers whose external validity to Scott’s grantees is exactly what
paper/review/rendered.txt:723:the realization factor is guessing at.
