192:Lifetime impact of GiveWell-directed donations to Top Charities
193-
194:From 2009 to 2024, GiveWell directed more than $1.45 billion to our
195:current Top Charities.1 We estimate that this funding will save a total
196-of about 340,000 lives by:
197-
198:- Distributing 101.2 million insecticide-treated nets to households
199:- Treating 76.1 million children with a full course of anti-malarial
200-  medicine
201:- Providing vitamin A supplements to 142.2 million children
202:- Vaccinating 1.0 million infants who wouldn’t have been vaccinated
203-  otherwise
