338-We update our cost-effectiveness models in an ongoing way as we learn
339-more or obtain new data, then finalize our cost-effectiveness estimate
340:for any given funding opportunity shortly before we make the grant to
341-that opportunity (or recommend it to a third party). We don’t go back
342-and update these estimates when our cost-effectiveness model changes.
