48:The Constellation Fund uses data and evidence to identify investments
49-that improve lifelong health and earnings for our neighbors. Our latest
50:Investment Report highlights what our portfolio of grantees achieved in
51:the fight against poverty across the Twin Cities — and why 2025 marks
52-our most productive year to date.
53-
54:DOWNLOAD 2025 REPORT (PDF)
