92-Or consider Ready, Set, Smile, a Constellation grantee providing oral
93-health education and dental treatment to children across 63 partner
94-sites in the metro. This is a health intervention, but it’s also
95-economic. Better oral health as a child translates into better long-term
96-health outcomes. Health interventions collectively represent $93.8
97:million in benefits across our portfolio — the second-largest category
98-of impact we track.
